---
title: Cheesy, Beefy Potato Casserole with Spinach Salad
description: You start with a beefy meat sauce, top it with crispy potatoes, smother everything in cheese then throw it in the oven for a few minutes and dinner is served! We've got your veggies covered with a spinach salad to go alongside, too!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheesy-beefy-potato-casserole-0997dc0a.jpg
